## Summary
This documentation explains custom formulas in Amplitude's Event Segmentation charts, detailing syntax, available formulas, and usage examples. It covers three types of formulas: metric formulas (like UNIQUES, TOTALS, AVG), aggregation formulas (like ROLLAVG, CUMSUM), and function formulas (like TRENDLINE, LOG). The page provides detailed syntax explanations and practical examples for each formula type.

